AP Physics 1: UNIFORM CIRCULAR MOTION, versionKey-01

prgmUNICIRMO
:Degree
:Input "_GRAVITY:_", G
:Disp ""
:Input "_MASS:_", M	//Only need Mass to find Tension
:Input "_RADIUS:_", R
:Input "_VELOC:_", V

:arctan(RG/V^2) --> Th
:MG/sin(Th) --> T
:2piR/V --> P
:R/cos(Th) --> L

:ClrHome
:Disp "_ROPE_LENGTH:", L
:Disp "_ <6 blanks> _TENSION:", T
:Disp "_ANGLE FROM HORIZ:", Th
:Disp "_ROTATION PERIOD (TP):", P
